    "interpretation": "Cardeep's discovered car-selling BUSINESS universe (33,690) exceeds the DIRCE-451 empresa count (14,367) ~2.3x. DIRCE counts only empresas whose PRINCIPAL activity is registered as 451; it undercounts autonomos, secondary-activity sellers, and informal points-of-sale. Therefore DIRCE-451 is a FLOOR/anchor, not a ceiling: it cannot serve as the sole capture-recapture denominator for the live retail universe. Coverage % >100% means saturation vs the formal registry, NOT a gap."
